theorem ext_iff {p q : exprℚ} : p = q ↔ p.num = q.num ∧ p.denom = q.denom :=
  by
  cases p
  cases q
  simp
#align ext_iff ext_iff
ext:
/- ./././Mathport/Syntax/Translate/Expr.lean:207:4: warning: unsupported notation `exprℚ -/
@[ext]
theorem ext {p q : exprℚ} (hn : p.num = q.num) (hd : p.denom = q.denom) : p = q :=
  rat.ext_iff.mpr ⟨hn, hd⟩
#align ext ext
